          <img src="https://cdn.defenseone.com/media/img/upload/2020/04/03/6030298/defense-large.jpg" alt="Capt. Brett Crozier, commanding officer of the aircraft carrier USS Theodore Roosevelt (CVN 71), addresses the crew Jan. 17, 2020" title="Capt. Brett Crozier, commanding officer of the aircraft carrier USS Theodore Roosevelt (CVN 71), addresses the crew Jan. 17, 2020">
        
      </div>

