            </div>
            The Battle of <span class="caps">USS</span> Theodore Roosevelt: a&nbsp;Timeline
          </a>
          </li>
        
          <li
            class="dont-miss-item  dont-miss-show
                   "
          >
          <a
            href="/ideas/2020/04/nato-should-always-work-home/164528/?oref=d-dontmiss"
            
            >
            <div>
              
              <img src="https://cdn.defenseone.com/media/img/upload/2020/04/10/nato_vidconf/thumb.jpg"
